  Ready to implement this plan?
  Choose how to leave Plan mode. The approved plan stays available in /work.

› 1. Implement now              Switch to Default mode and start coding.
  2. Start fresh and implement  Fresh thread with this plan.
  3. Keep planning              Stay in Plan mode with the current thread.

  Press enter to confirm or esc to go back
